c-6d94db8fbcbd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-83c3bc0a-9666-45cc-b452-9fa9f94f0241\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fd05dfa9-d401-4ddf-b432-1b0898dff926\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d939831a-8678-4418-a35c-e1066255698d\">아! 맛있는 단감을 먹기전에 우리 단감의 효능을 한번 알아볼까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-91d28b8e-047f-4e00-a44a-61d0e346085e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2680c9bc-2100-4064-894a-c9fe6081a974\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6d914e8f-5188-4dbc-933f-960bcde2a034\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0a1f61b9-8ff6-454a-b5ff-ca3315db1f96\">일단은, 단감은 항암효과가 뛰어나고 비타민C가 풍부해서 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-26d0df7a-609a-45c7-bd57-87c3eb22a148\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c77c2e8-464d-4c2d-aa23-681c990f355a\">아침 저녁으로 일교차가 심한 환절기 감기예방에 좋다고 하네요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5f2850df-aa72-4aff-b566-6a85f5376878\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-48ba4b05-db99-4705-8c19-5b7034e684fc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c2e44233-a019-4922-917a-6f6b459e859f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-db8df471-bb08-451f-921b-ee80caced40d\"><b>1. 피부미용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-29dc8a7b-c211-4623-a14d-b26b9de8e4ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27dc9a28-e950-4847-b33a-f7d8bcbb1f72\">단감에 함유된 비타민C는 사과에 비해 10배나 넘게 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-690d00ff-5350-4a66-913a-cee176ab33d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fa110d84-a5fe-48a6-af78-1281d4915b53\">풍부한 비타민C가 피부에게 영양을 공급해주고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0709bf93-44e6-4207-af7b-1e247bda9a2c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e933488b-51d4-4345-a551-3dda45d46ac6\">피부노화를 일으키는 활성산소를 제거해주는 효과를 보여줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-91b02598-933f-49be-813b-0f04e1c26348\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2f82ebae-158e-4f04-bac5-9b460ff79a53\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-92753b95-ffd0-4545-b64b-265e7c9b13e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b9a99430-22b8-4d3a-93d4-d02a3f368cf3\"><b>2. 비타민 부족 해소</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-451d7ddc-907d-4bbc-b8ca-e47265c51b73\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1f022c88-ce6a-4fbf-aa4d-c72bd13e7cd5\">가을에 천연보약이라고 할만큼 여러가지 영양소가 많은 과일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f7879614-5099-4653-972f-5d6f2e106d6c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-454cdeb1-0fe8-4daa-838c-1ba18f715dc1\">그중에서도 비타민이 다양하고 풍부해서 천연비타민을 다양하게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b30a72d-c394-4ae2-a5e6-b6d9b72c1b20\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b24a7dc6-86f4-4b82-95d8-37c5b893254c\">섭취할수있게 도와주는 아주 좋은 과일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da2f8f15-2a2e-4f72-bcbd-8443a4ab1f9c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6cf2505c-310d-4f67-9f32-4279645d03f7\"> 그 밖에도 비타민A, C, 베타카로틴이 풍부해서 피로회복, 감기예방,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c4cd960a-35a2-4842-9eff-6f84086bb1fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-da880690-16a7-462d-81a0-2c0cfe76e035\">눈건강을 지켜주는 우리몸에 아주 좋은 과일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-250da913-c5a1-4a05-9a6b-1714e0db8cf8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-737e14fd-3839-4202-ac9e-7bb4a36048fa\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c58169e7-8041-468f-944d-4b63537eb106\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4eb57b55-8225-4c57-adcb-1f53b23dfd92\"><b>3. 다이어트에 효과적</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb305281-c802-405f-93f4-81593a118823\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c89d7820-a500-43aa-aefb-4e2239913da0\">단감은 칼로리가 낮아서 포만감을 높여주고 식사량을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6667fbd9-fe74-4cf8-86cb-04d3c1fb616c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-725f9476-80ed-4d43-8a61-8dc89db4efd0\">조절할때에도 좋고, 펙틴이라는 성분이 풍부하게 들어있어서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-666757e3-c1fc-4c09-9849-564bb07fc779\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4e649e5c-8b3d-4bd9-9f4d-c9c4d2a0e739\">중성지방, 콜레스테롤을 몸밖으로 배출하게 하는 효과가 있어 다이어트에도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-67ff0438-4da2-4ec9-8b0d-df268453b550\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aa67b6ca-1ef6-4d56-b58a-3dba57457431\">좋은 과일입니다. 그리고, 식이 섬유가 엄청 풍부해서 변비에도 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-89339f61-94d7-4bd6-b6d7-c027ced13460\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9fe88de8-e168-4580-977a-72a4d87a3118\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a39398b8-d4cd-406b-ba91-3a0f7db3794e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27119259-61e1-44c1-937b-4228a9de7bee\"><b>4. 눈건강</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e6f6bfdd-31e0-4922-8a0e-078cb5e0a7cc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ef983805-c905-4e56-a85a-4fe1da050554\">단감은 과일중에서도 비타민A가 매우 풍부하게 들어있는 과일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f261d979-fa30-4fde-a638-f35df632621f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6a8ff5b-f004-4a83-a375-f6fe06b9ac9d\">비타민A로 노화로 인해 생기는 망막색소 결핍증을 예방해주고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd92aad0-e29c-4e45-90a4-f4f79edd2ac9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6e0c601e-b8bf-4c97-a7ed-f738882678ea\">시력이 악화되지 않도록 해주며, 강막이 건조해지는것과 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e758865c-5c40-492b-baf1-5f9ec6f3959a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d552c9fa-eb3c-49d6-93f8-8430d2e1ae46\">황반변성이 일어나는것을 예방해주는 효과가있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e0e11b2b-4d7a-434f-9214-8ba7f3b82dd2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7545bb7f-ae80-48d3-b7bd-6ca756c100d1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f197341-9bcf-4c28-b0e8-56a3137b1d8d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f45bc59-bae9-4300-9cbe-a6fd78cdb9c2\"><b>5. 혈관질환예방</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4ef181fe-98bc-4143-a084-1ab0131b1203\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7ed5753-7c26-40d5-beb0-9322a229a826\">단감은 고혈압이나 동맥경화등의 혈관질환들에 예방하는데 도움을 준다고 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e57a4edb-07e8-46fa-8b1d-1ea2adbcb38a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b68ac84-53f1-4e42-8620-4357e4321bb6\">단감에 함유된 스코폴린틴이라고 불리는 성분이 혈관의 벽을 튼튼하게 해주는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7e359e71-8f7e-4344-bf5d-883f0b4deb7a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d982e6d6-7a3c-415f-9132-1a4b3b35d72a\">작용을 해줘서 혈관질환예방에 매우 훌륭한 효과을 보여줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c0469ded-c3ef-4d41-ad0c-ad37ae7ef320\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8c5fa4d1-3725-46a0-8ec5-200ebdc68a9f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9112da69-d645-4eb9-8fa0-4ce5cd41893e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae3f8008-6996-4e5b-9740-d36f9c8b0ab0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-44640921-ca77-4430-a7f5-4363f8396e8b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27a65f31-3c35-4e3e-9e48-c420ee843af8\">이렇게 알고 드시면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8c4d5360-b88a-451c-bebd-921f3cd0620f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dba7c7b7-e2c4-4c69-b730-a9e506a42d58\">맛있는 단감이 더욱 더 맛있겠죠?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0fc343cf-da27-44f6-8963-96e911673eed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65911fad-6824-4161-b5d5-a5edb5ba7fc3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e334971-b865-4ecd-b9c2-03fa4bb908ff\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-827c19cf-37a4-4663-bb2c-bf762435e4c2\">이번 가을에 맛있는 단감 맛있게 드시고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ea9a9651-7bd8-4ec6-9318-55397c4865d2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-873ccc04-c119-415a-a620-fc84ea4d0de4\">모두 건강하세요!! </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1f0a2fef-3f37-478b-bb02-4db9f33036bd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-41989be3-e4d6-4f98-a837-cf40d86a4eef\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-949919f7-d4f1-40f7-89b6-ee0141f80600\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"https: